Package: BART4RS
Type: Package
Title: BART for Additive Hazards Survival Models
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Antonio Linero
Maintainer: Antonio Linero <antonio.linero@austin.utexas.edu>
Description: This package fits Bayesian nonparametric additive hazards survival 
    models. The primary function uses a piecewise-exponential baseline hazard
    model combined with a BART model to fit a proportional hazards model to
    the excess hazard function.
License: GPL Version 2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
